# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  Dhara — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database ──
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=dhara
DB_USER=dhara
DB_PASSWORD=password
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://dhara:password@localhost:5432/dhara

# ── Redis ──
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ── MinIO (Object Storage) ──
MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://localhost:9000
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=minioadmin
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=minioadmin
MINIO_BUCKET=dhara-documents

# ── Kafka ──
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP=localhost:9092

# ── JWT Authentication ──
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-in-production

# ── gRPC (Backend → RAG Service) ──
RAG_SERVICE_HOST=localhost
RAG_SERVICE_PORT=50051

# ── LLM Provider (ollama, deepseek, gemini, claude, openai) ──
LLM_PROVIDER=ollama
LLM_ROUTER_MODE=local
# LLM_ROUTER_PROVIDERS=["deepseek", "gemini", "claude"]

# ── Ollama (runs natively, not in Docker) ──
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen3:14b

# ── API Keys (fill for production) ──
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=
DEEPSEEK_MODEL=deepseek-chat
GEMINI_API_KEY=
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
OPENAI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
COHERE_API_KEY=

# ── Embedding Provider (bgem3, ollama, openai) ──
EMBEDDING_PROVIDER=bgem3
EMBEDDING_DIMENSION=1024
BGEM3_MODEL_PATH=BAAI/bge-m3
BGEM3_USE_FP16=true
OLLAMA_EMBEDDING_MODEL=nomic-embed-text

# ── Reranker Provider (bge, cohere, noop) ──
RERANKER_PROVIDER=bge
RERANKER_TOP_K=5

# ── Search Weights ──
SEARCH_VECTOR_WEIGHT=0.6
SEARCH_BM25_WEIGHT=0.4
SEARCH_TOP_K=10

# ── SSLCommerz (Payment) ──
SSLCOMMERZ_STORE_ID=
SSLCOMMERZ_STORE_PASSWORD=
SSLCOMMERZ_SANDBOX=true

# ── Frontend ──
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
NEXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_LOCALE=bn

# ── Server Ports ──
SERVER_PORT=8080
